        "user_id": 184228714,
        "body": "Good evening, colleagues.\nI’m looking at vanna levels, and I see a large cluster around 6500.\n\nQuestion for those who actively trade Greeks:\nHow strong do you think vanna really is?\nDo you consider it critically important compared to gamma and charm?\nDo you view it as a standalone level or more as an additional filter when vol starts moving?",
