        "raw_body": "I think it all depends on the context of positioning with the other Greeks. There’s theoretically hedging formulas for MMs on all of these that an algo can calculate to get the closest to delta neutral as possible and I would guess it entirely depends on those interactions within the MMs portfolio (MM options positioning of overall market)",
        "user_pub_role": null,
        "most_recent_comment_created_at": null,
        "mediaAttachments": []
      },
